{"word":"G1282 - διαπρίω - diapríō - dee-ap-ree'-o - Cut","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαπρίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diapríō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ap-ree'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cut</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மூர்க்கமடை"},{"paragraph":"to saw asunder or in twain, to divide by a saw: to be sawn through mentally, to be torn with vexation cut to the heart"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G4249 - πρίζω - prízō - prid'-zo/4249\">G4249</a>; to <i>saw asunder</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>exasperate:</i> - cut (to the heart).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}